resources NO(4)
notes
The joint Norwegian-Ukrainian SSISS (Self-Scattering and Ion Sound Stimulation)
experiment is aimed at two principal goals:
1. Study of self-scattering of powerful HF waves on pump-stimulated plasma
inhomogeneities;
2. IS radar study of HF pump-stimulated ion acoustic waves.

